                <head>37. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>From October 27 to November 16, the Foreign Ministers of the United States, the
                    United Kingdom, France, and the Soviet Union met at Geneva. For documentation on
                    United States participation in this conference, and on Secretary <persName
                        corresp="#p_DJF1">Dulles</persName>’ subsequent reports to the President and
                    the National Security Council, see volume V.</p>
            </div>
